      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels that can still get the job done? This car isn\u2019t perfect and I\u2019d rather be upfront about that, but it\u2019s an affordable option for someone who wants basic transport, a project, or a handy runaround. It\u2019s priced fairly for what it is, and if you appreciate a straightforward sale from someone honest, this could be a great little opportunity.",
