      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong project or budget-driver opportunity with solid core mechanicals and the kind of analog feel enthusiasts appreciate. The engine pulls cleanly, the transmission engages as it should, and the chassis still feels usable for someone looking for inexpensive transportation or a hands-on refurb candidate. Cosmetic wear and age-related needs are present, but it remains a straightforward platform with good parts value and real upside for the next owner. Priced to move for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at.",
