    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Here\u2019s a car with real character\u2014an honest, well-traveled machine that still has plenty of story left to tell. It\u2019s the kind of vehicle that appeals to someone who sees opportunity where others see age: a dependable canvas for a daily runabout, weekend project, or practical backup ride. With a presence that feels seasoned rather than ordinary, it offers affordable entry into ownership and the chance to make it your own without a huge upfront spend.",
