      "description": "An affordable opportunity for a value-focused buyer, this vehicle offers straightforward transportation at an accessible price point. It shows its age cosmetically and mechanically, but it remains a practical choice for someone seeking inexpensive mobility, a project car, or a spare vehicle. Priced to reflect its condition and deliver strong budget value.",
