    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels that won\u2019t break the bank? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who needs basic transportation, a project, or a handy extra vehicle to have around. It\u2019s priced with its condition in mind and offers a lot of value for the money. If you\u2019re realistic, practical, and want something inexpensive with plenty of life left to give, this could be a great fit. Come take a look and see if it suits what you need.",
